%section#policy.main

  %h2 Privacy Policy
  %p
    Your privacy is very important to us. We have developed this Policy in order
    for you to understand how we collect, use, communicate and disclose and make
    use of personal information. The following outlines our privacy policy.
  %p
    By using Hound.cc, you agree to the collection and use of your personal
    information as described in this policy. You should know:

  %ul
    %li
      We automatically delete your email contents after the reminder has been
      sent, as well as your recipient's email address. To provide for the
      ability to reschedule a reminder that has been sent, deletion may occur
      several days or weeks following the completion of the followup.
    %li
      We collect limited account information to maintain your account and reminders
      on our servers.
    %li
      We will never rent, sell or share information that personally identifies you
      for marketing purposes without your express permission.
    %li You can update your account information and preferences at any time
    %li
      We will send reminder emails as requested by Hound.cc users. We may send
      emails about enhancements to hound.cc of tips and ways of using the system.
    %li
      You can unsubscribe from all mailings at any time by emailing us at
      = mail_to 'support@hound.cc'
    %li
      Neither Hound.cc nor any third party associated with Hound.cc will ever
      send you unsolicited emails not directly related to providing assistance
      or improving your service experience. If If you know of or are experiencing
      any abuse of the Hound.cc system, please contact us at
      = mail_to 'support@hound.cc'
    %li
      This website uses of cookies and track the behavior of its users using custom
      and industry standard analytics tools such as Google Analytics.
    %li
      Hound.cc is very concerned with safeguarding your information. We employ
      reasonable measures designed to protect your information from unauthorized
      access.
    %li
      Personal information collected by Hound.cc may be stored and processed in the
      United States, the United Kingdom, or any other country in which Hound.cc and its infrastructure providers
      maintain facilities. By using Hound.cc, you consent to any such transfer of
      information outside of your country.

    %li
      We reserve the right to transfer your personal information in the event of a
      transfer of ownership of Hound.cc, such as acquisition by or merger with another
      company. In such an event, Hound.cc will notify you with an opt-out option
      before information is transferred and becomes subject to a different privacy
      policy.
    %li
      To comply with the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act, at this time
      Hound.cc is only available to users who are at least 13 years old. If you
      are under 13, please do not use the Hound.cc service.
    %li
      We may amend this Privacy Policy from time to time, at our sole discretion.
      Use of information we collect now is subject to the Privacy Policy in effect
      at the time such information is used.
    %li
      If we make changes to the Privacy Policy, we will notify you by posting an
      announcement on the hound.cc website so you are always aware of what
      information we collect, how we use it, and under what circumstances if any, it is disclosed.

  %p
    If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
    = mail_to 'support@hound.cc'

